Nov 9 (Reuters) - Amazon.com Inc AMZN.O:: *AMAZON AND WEBER FILE JOINT LAWSUIT AGAINST COUNTERFEITERS *AMAZON.COM INC - FILED A LAWSUIT AGAINST 12 DEFENDANTS FOR SELLING PRODUCTS THAT ILLEGALLY BEAR WEBER® REGISTERED TRADEMARK IN AMAZON'S STORE *AMAZON.COM INC - AMAZON CLOSED DEFENDANTS' SELLING ACCOUNTS AND PROACTIVELY REFUNDED IMPACTED CUSTOMERS
